		<call text="&#34;Afficher &#34;&#34;les 6 meilleurs chiffres sorties le plus souvent sont\n %d, %d, %d, %d, %d, %d\n&#34;&#34;,&#34;,&#34;  tbMostWinning[0], tbMostWinning[1], tbMostWinning[2], tbMostWinning[3], tbMostWinning[4], tbMostWinning[5]&#34;" comment="" color="ffff80" disabled="0"></call>
